title: EditBone 12.6.6 Portable 32-bit
description:
EditBone 12.6.6 Portable 32-bit




32-bit software can be used on 64-bit machines as well.


Download, unzip and use.  It is portable and free too.  Enjoy!



Text And Code Editor

EditBone is a code and text editor that offers syntax highlighting for more than 50 scripting languages. In addition to standard editing features, it offers page bookmarks, line/word/character count, line sorting, search & replace and browser preview.
The program can also be used to compare the content of two files. You can view the differences in a side-by-side view and copy changes from one file to the other.
EditBone also includes a macro recorder that enables you to record frequently typed text to quickly insert it later.
